com.google.appinventor.client

Interface Images

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ClientBundle, Tree.Resources

    public interface Images
extends Tree.Resources
    Image bundle containing all client images. Note: Images extends Tree.Resources rather than ClientBundle so that the Images can be used with the com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Tree class.
